    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nahze tee Gada Behrni/ un tee Rubbexa Behrni/un run- naja us Mohſu/un us Eeleasaru to Preestert/ un us tahs Drau-dses Wirfneekem / un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atarota/ un Dibons / un Jaesers/ un Nimra/ un Esbons/ un Eeleale/ un Sebena/ un Ne-ba/ un Beona.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Semme/ ko tas Kungs fittis irr preekſch tahs Israëta Draudses / irr weena Semme preekſch gannameem Pulkeem / un muus taweem Kalpeem irr gammami Pulki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee fazzija : Ja mehs Schehlastibu eſſam atradduschi tawas Azzis/ laid fchi Seimme taweem Kalpeem dohta tohp par Jhpaschumu / un ne leeſ muhs pahreet pahr to Jardann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Mohsus fazzija us teem Gada Behrneem / un us teem Rubbexa Behrneem: Ar-rig tad juhsfu Brahti Karrâ ees? un juhs fche palikfeet?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rapehz juhs lauschat teem Israëta Behrneem to Sirdi? ka tee ue no-eet us to Semmi/ fo tas KUNgs winneem dewis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta darrija juhsfo Tehwi/ kad es tohs fuhtiju no Kahdes-Barneas to Semmi apluhkoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tee bija nahkufchi pee tahs Eskota Eelejas/ un to Sem-mi bij isluhkojſchi/ tad lausija tee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "to Israëta Behrnu Sirđi/ka tee ne gribbeja eet us to Semmi/ fo tas KUNGS winneem gribbe- ja doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad apskaitahs ta KUNG-GA Bahrsiba tai Deenâ / un wiꞥſch swehreja/ un fazzija :\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teem Laudim/ kas no E-giptes-Semmes irr nahkufchi / no diwidesmits Gaddeem un pah- ri / ne buhs to Semmi redeht/ ko Es winxo Tehweem Abbra-amam/ Ihsackam un Jehkabam swehrejis efmu / jo tee ne irr man pakkaufjuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bes ween Kahlebs Je-wuxa Dehls tas Kenisiteris/ un Josuüs Nunna Dehls/ jo tee irr tam KUNGAH klaufjuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta apskaitahs ta KUNG-GA Bahrsiba prett Israëlu/ un likte tohs bohkstitees Tukfnefi tschetrdefinitis Gaddus / teekams wiſſi Augumi bohja gabje / kas taunu bija darrijuschi / preekſch ta KUNGA Azzim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu raugi/ juhs effat juhsfo Tehwu Weetâ nahkufchi / weens Pulks grehzigu Zilweku / wairodami ta KUNGA bahrgu Dufmibu prett Israëlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ja juhs atgreesifeetees no winna pakkanes / tad liks wiꞥſch wehl schohs Tukfnefi pa-likt/ un juhs nomaitafeet wiſſus schohs Laudis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad peegahje tee pee wiſ-na/ un fazzija : Mehs gribbam ſcheit Laidarus taiſht preekſch muhfu gannameem Pulkeem un Pils-\n"
    }
  ],
